        'operations.hero.title': 'Operations & Setup',
      'operations.hero.desc': 'A section dedicated to all cards that are not â€œproductsâ€: opening, display set-up, packaging, service procedures and closing. Here you\'ll find the standards that keep the counter clean, fast and consistent.',
      'operations.hero.coverAlt': 'Badiani operations playbook',

